    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Proofs retained by the artist, similar to artist's proofs, although they are usually separate or additional publications. Can also generally refer to three-dimensional objects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047306/Gemini G.E.L. [online] (2005)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Proeven die door de kunstenaar worden behouden, vergelijkbaar met afdrukken voor de kunstenaar, hoewel het meestal afzonderlijke of aanvullende publicaties betreft. Kan ook in algemene zin verwijzen naar driedimensionale objecten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>由藝術家保存的印版樣張，與試版樣張(artist's proofs)相似，儘管其通常是獨立或附加的刊物。一般也可用於指稱立體物件。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
